needs arduino 1.5.8

get arduino ide
1. download [arduino ide for udoo](http://www.udoo.org/downloads/#tab4) and move it to {arduino_dir}
2. create symlink to arduino: sudo ln -s {arduino_dir} /usr/share/arduino
3. replace syscalls_sam3.c by syscalls_sam3.cbak in {arduino_dir}/hardware/arduino/sam/cores/arduino/

get ino
1. git clone https://github.com/justonia/ino.git --branch ide1.5x
2. git apply --ignore-space-change --ignore-whitespace patch
3. sudo make install

if permission denied errors run the scripts as sudo or follow these steps to aquire write permissions
1. sudo chown -RL {user} /sys/class/gpio
2. sudo chown /dev/ttymxc3
